parameters.name: EndpointId
parameters.description: The ID of the gateway endpoint.

parameters.name: EndpointName
parameters.description:
The name of the gateway endpoint.

The name must be 1 to 128 characters in length.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: The number of entries to return per page. Valid values: **1** to **100**. Default value: **20**.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description:
The pagination token that is used in the next request to retrieve a new page of results. Valid values:

*   You do not need to specify this parameter for the first request.
*   If a value is returned for NextToken, specify the value in the next request to retrieve a new page of results.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description:
The region ID of the gateway endpoint.

You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~36063~~) operation to query the most recent region list.

parameters.name: ResourceGroupId
parameters.description: The ID of the resource group to which the gateway endpoint belongs.

parameters.name: ServiceName
parameters.description: The name of the endpoint service.

parameters.name: VpcId
parameters.description: The ID of the virtual private cloud (VPC) to which the gateway endpoint belongs.
